# Nucleotide Sequence Retrieval

This repository section contains nucleotide sequence datasets retrieved from NCBI for practical bioinformatics analysis and computational biology workflows.

## Contents

The folder currently contains:

- FASTA format nucleotide sequences
- GenBank annotation files
- Sequence-specific subdirectories
- NCBI accession-based organization structure

## Applications

These nucleotide sequences can be utilized for:

- BLAST analysis
- Multiple sequence alignment
- Mutation and variant analysis
- Phylogenetic tree construction
- Gene annotation studies

## Data Source

NCBI Nucleotide Database
